General.Name: Tessin Nordic Holding AB
General.Description: Tessin Nordic Holding AB (publ) owns and operates a digital investment platform for property financing. Its platform links property developers seeking loan financing with investors seeking exposure to a high-return asset class with balanced risk, as well as backed by collateral primarily property mortgages. The company primarily offers construction and bridge loans to property companies and property developers. Tessin Nordic Holding AB (publ) was founded in 2014 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
